extends layout

block append content
	h1 Parties
	a(href="booking.html", class="btn btn-primary") Book Your Party Now!
	h2 The Fun Time Magic Show
	p.
		This is a 45 minute magic and puppet show designed to engage and
		entertain children from 3-10 years. Right from the beginning of the
		show there is fun, laughter, juggling and magic as Michael uses
		his special scanner to find the Birthday boy/girl in the audience.
		They then get to take a staring role in the show and help make the magic
		work with hilarious consequences.
	img(src="src/images/party.jpg", alt="Children enjoying one of Michael's parties", class="img-responsive hidden-print")
	h2 Superhero Magic Party
	p.
		This is also a 45 minute magic show themed around Superheroes. Fun is
		guaranteed as the children help Michael and his superhero friend Magic
		Marvel defeat the evil Dr Doom! This party is aimed for children aged
		5 - 10.
	img(src="src/images/superhero.jpg", alt="Magic Marvel", class="img-responsive hidden-print")
	h2 Details
	ul
		li All birthday party packages will be adapted according to age and gender
		li A special balloon hat creation and wand or likewise are provided for the special boy/girl.
		li Pre-School and School shows are also available, as well as XMas Themed Shows.
		li Michael is fully CRB checked.
	p 45 minute party packages only cost &pound;100!
	a(href="booking.html", class="btn btn-primary btn-lg") Book Now!